    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Can't find any reference to anchor.js anymore, are we just using pure anchors?\n\nI can definitely reproduce the bad behavior when opening in a new tab and waiting for it to load.\n\nMaybe we could force the url back again when the tab get focused (if we have an event). That would be a quick and dirty fix.\n\nThis bug may be due to the fact that the page height changes when the widgets are initialized.\n",
