    "body": "> This bug may be due to the fact that the page height changes when the widgets are initialized.\n\nYep, I think that's the case. Nice catch. Listening to the tab select might work if such an event is easily accessible, or waiting for all the widgets to instanciate before scrolling to the url again.\n",
